casebody.data:
No. 10-7441. Arturo Solis, Petitioner v. Texas Department of Criminal Justice. 562 U.S. 1130, 131 S. Ct. 979,

178 L. Ed. 2d 742,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 552. January 10, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Texas, Tenth Circuit, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
